contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentLabel: Kentico FAQs: Understanding Versions and Services Naming
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentShortDescription: Kentico community member, Milan Lund, helps us understand some of the less discussed topics of the Kentico world. What's up with all the product names, what is a Kentico partner, and how do we upgrade to Xperience by Kentico?
